": 324, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of the sporting fraternity, Olympians, administrators and sponsors, were brought together at theObserver'sBeechwood Avenue headquarters in Kingston as the media group highlighted its coverage plans that include insightful, on-the-ground reporting - which has already started with the pre-Olympic camp currently under way in Stuttgart, Germany as well as stride-by-stride accounts of the Olympic Games itself that run from July 26 to August 11 in the French capital - through radio, print, video, online and social media executions.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\", \"score\": 0.999999999917236, \"rank\": 8.27841212155939e-11, \"text\": \"Kingston\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingston_upon_Thames\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"score\": 0.9999999290998883, \"rank\": 4.3269392987125415e-08, \"text\": \"Stuttgart\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stuttgart\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9981527306304239, \"rank\": 0.0011041640010607395, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Members\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting fraternity\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"administrators\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"theObserver'sBeechwood Avenue headquarters\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 495}, {\"n