m\": 1403, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"packaging\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to extend my deepest gratitude to all our sponsors and partners whose support must be seen as a resounding vote of confidence in not only our credibility and reputation as a First World media organisation, but also our ability to deliver unparalleled storytelling as well as the best offering in terms of comprehensive, easily digestible, and engaging coverage of our athletes and everything relating to the Paris 2024 Games,\\\" Beaubrun added.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1892, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaubrun_Ardouin\", \"score\": 0.999999986966941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beaubrun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaubrun_Ardouin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beaubrun_Ardouin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my deepest gratitude\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"all our sponsors\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"whose support\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"a resounding vote\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"not only our credibility\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"reputation\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"a First World media organisation\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"unparalleled storytelling\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the best offering\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheObserver'steam in France will be led by experienced reporter Robert Bailey and photographer Naphatli Junior, with support from Keith McGhie and photographer/digital content creator Leo Hudson.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9971647012171089, \"rank\": 0.0016760811648347128, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bailey_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.5205024780554159, \"rank\": 0.8275862068966597, \"text\": \"Robert Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bailey_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bailey_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\", \"score\": 0.9982402254448414, \"rank\": 0.0011269287925729475, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheObserver'steam\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"Naphatli Junior\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"Keith McGhie\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will provide full coverage including radio, video, online, social media and print properties.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full coverage\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"radio, video, online, social media and print properties\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These will include in-print features and reports; podcasts; live updates and commentary onEDGE 105 FM; social media giveaways and 